{"analytics_identifier":"OT1459","base_path":"/government/organisations/regulatory-innovation-office","content_id":"62aad2ff-f427-43dc-a0be-3327baacbdbd","description":"The Regulatory Innovation Office (RIO) updates regulation, speeds up approval times and ensures regulatory bodies work together effectively. RIO is part of the Department for Science, Innovation and Technology .","details":{"acronym":"RIO","alternative_format_contact_email":"alt.formats@dsit.gov.uk","body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The Regulatory Innovation Office (RIO) updates regulation, speeds up approval times and ensures regulatory bodies work together effectively.</p>\n\n<p><abbr title=\"Regulatory Innovation Office\">RIO</abbr> is part of the <a class=\"brand__color\" href=\"/government/organisations/department-for-science-innovation-and-technology\">Department for Science, Innovation and Technology</a>.</p>\n</div>","brand":"department-for-science-innovation-technology","foi_exempt":false,"logo":{"crest":"single-identity","formatted_title":"Regulatory Innovation Office"},"ordered_corporate_information_pages":[{"href":"/government/organisations/regulatory-innovation-office/about/accessible-documents-policy","title":"Accessible documents policy"},{"href":"/government/organisations/regulatory-innovation-office/about/complaints-procedure","title":"Complaints procedure"},{"href":"/government/organisations/regulatory-innovation-office/about/media-enquiries","title":"Media enquiries"}],"ordered_featured_documents":[{"document_type":"Press release","href":"/government/news/red-tape-to-be-slashed-for-british-robotics-and-defence-innovators","image":{"alt_text":"Driving British robotics and defence innovation.","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6969f75b1c8a70fc0a3b0445/s712_driving-robotics-defence-innovation-rio-govuk.png","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6969f75bcbe2202b38424889/s465_driving-robotics-defence-innovation-rio-govuk.png","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6969f75b7b7f37aa8e4022c7/driving-robotics-defence-innovation-rio-govuk.png"},"public_updated_at":"2026-01-16T00:00:00.000+00:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>Robotics and defence tech announced as the RIO’s 2 new priority areas.</p>\n</div>","title":"Red tape to be slashed for British robotics and defence innovators"}],"ordered_featured_links":[],"ordered_promotional_features":[],"organisation_featuring_priority":"news","organisation_govuk_status":{"status":"live","updated_at":null,"url":null},"organisation_political":false,"organisation_type":"sub_organisation","secondary_corporate_information_pages":"","social_media_links":[]},"document_type":"organisation","first_published_at":"2025-10-15T14:40:02+01:00","links":{"available_translations":[{"analytics_identifier":"OT1459","api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/regulatory-innovation-office","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/organisations/regulatory-innovation-office","base_path":"/government/organisations/regulatory-innovation-office","content_id":"62aad2ff-f427-43dc-a0be-3327baacbdbd","document_type":"organisation","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2025-10-21T07:48:26Z","schema_name":"organisation","title":"Regulatory Innovation Office","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/regulatory-innovation-office","withdrawn":false}],"ordered_board_members":[{"api_path":"/api/content/government/people/david-willetts","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/people/david-willetts","base_path":"/government/people/david-willetts","content_id":"852929e8-c0f1-11e4-8223-005056011aef","details":{"image":{"alt_text":"The Rt Hon Lord David Willetts","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/5a4f67efe5274a6bed6136ea/s465_David-Willetts-960x640.jpg"},"privy_counsellor":true},"document_type":"person","links":{"role_appointments":[{"content_id":"31b1e751-056f-4b91-9c0d-1385700dd944","details":{"current":true,"ended_on":null,"person_appointment_order":2,"started_on":"2025-03-07T00:00:00+00:00"},"document_type":"role_appointment","links":{"role":[{"content_id":"a2008076-e5e2-4968-9af8-e3919494603a","details":{"body":"<p>Working with officials and ministers, the Chair of the <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/regulatory-innovation-office\">Regulatory Innovation Office</a> (<abbr title=\"Regulatory Innovation Office\">RIO</abbr>) provides leadership and direction to the <abbr title=\"Regulatory Innovation Office\">RIO</abbr>. The <abbr title=\"Regulatory Innovation Office\">RIO</abbr> is an office within the Department for Science, Innovation and Technology (<abbr title=\"Department for Science, Innovation and Technology\">DSIT</abbr>) that helps reduce the burden for businesses bringing new products to the market in some of the UK’s fastest-growing sectors.</p>\n\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2026-03-18T14:41:28Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Chair: Regulatory Innovation Office","withdrawn":false}]},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2025-10-21T15:45:11Z","schema_name":"role_appointment","title":"The Rt Hon Lord David Willetts - Chair: Regulatory Innovation Office","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"882dccce-6aae-48fa-be3e-5b76f325bf57","details":{"current":false,"ended_on":"2014-07-14T00:00:00+01:00","person_appointment_order":27,"started_on":"2010-05-12T00:00:00+01:00"},"document_type":"role_appointment","links":{"role":[{"api_path":"/api/content/government/ministers/minister-of-state-universities-and-science-department-for-business-innovation-and-skills","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/ministers/minister-of-state-universities-and-science-department-for-business-innovation-and-skills","base_path":"/government/ministers/minister-of-state-universities-and-science-department-for-business-innovation-and-skills","content_id":"845e6a06-c0f1-11e4-8223-005056011aef","details":{"body":"<div class=\"call-to-action\">\n  <p>In December 2018, the role of Minister of State for Universities and Science was replaced by the role of <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/people/chris-skidmore\">Minister of State for Universities, Science, Research and Innovation</a>.</p>\n</div>\n\n<p>The minister is responsible for:</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"higher-education\">Higher education</h2>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>widening participation for students and providers</li>\n  <li>student finance</li>\n  <li>education exports strategy</li>\n  <li>preventing violent extremism</li>\n  <li>international students and migration</li>\n  <li>student experience</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2 id=\"science-and-research\">Science and research</h2>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>research funding</li>\n  <li>postgraduates</li>\n  <li>public engagement in science</li>\n  <li>STEM (science technology, engineering and mathematics) skills</li>\n  <li>open access / research data</li>\n  <li>relationship with Government Office for Science on science in policy</li>\n  <li>Newton Fund</li>\n  <li>Agri-Tech industrial strategy</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2 id=\"innovation-and-commerce\">Innovation and commerce</h2>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>Innovate UK and innovation partners</li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/eight-great-technologies-infographics\">eight great technologies</a></li>\n  <li>smart cities</li>\n  <li>space</li>\n  <li>public sector research establishments</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Note that, until May 2015, this ministerial role also included responsibility for cities policy and local and regional growth.</p>\n","role_payment_type":null,"seniority":9,"whip_organisation":{}},"document_type":"ministerial_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2019-04-05T12:13:28Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Minister of State for Universities and Science","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/ministers/minister-of-state-universities-and-science-department-for-business-innovation-and-skills","withdrawn":false}]},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2019-11-08T16:14:04Z","schema_name":"role_appointment","title":"The Rt Hon David Willetts - Minister of State for Universities and Science","withdrawn":false}]},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2025-03-31T15:52:37Z","schema_name":"person","title":"The Rt Hon Lord David Willetts","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/people/david-willetts","withdrawn":false}],"ordered_contacts":[{"content_id":"c92f5553-9128-4b91-9fd6-ee784a291558","details":{"contact_form_links":null,"description":null,"email_addresses":null,"phone_numbers":null,"post_addresses":[{"iso2_country_code":"gb","locality":"London","postal_code":"SW1A 2EG","street_address":"Department for Science, Innovation and Technology\r\n22-26 Whitehall","title":"Regulatory Innovation Office ","world_location":"United Kingdom"}],"title":"General enquiries"},"document_type":"contact","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2025-10-21T09:43:14Z","schema_name":"contact","title":"General enquiries","withdrawn":false}],"ordered_foi_contacts":[{"content_id":"95c15f57-0a3e-4964-a463-47c3770dafe7","details":{"contact_form_links":null,"description":null,"email_addresses":[{"email":"foi@dsit.gov.uk","title":"Information Rights and Records Unit"}],"phone_numbers":null,"post_addresses":[{"iso2_country_code":"gb","locality":"London","postal_code":"SW1H 0ET","street_address":"Department for Science, Innovation and Technology\r\n1 Victoria Street","title":"Information Rights and Records Unit","world_location":"United Kingdom"}],"title":"Freedom of information contacts"},"document_type":"contact","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2025-10-21T09:47:09Z","schema_name":"contact","title":"Freedom of information contacts","withdrawn":false}],"ordered_parent_organisations":[{"analytics_identifier":"D1381","api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/department-for-science-innovation-and-technology","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/